11#include "ipf.h"
12
13#include <syslog.h>
14
15
16void
17printlog(fp)
18 frentry_t *fp;
19{
20 char *s, *u;
21
22 PRINTF("log");
23 if (fp->fr_flags & FR_LOGBODY)
24 PRINTF(" body");
25 if (fp->fr_flags & FR_LOGFIRST)
26 PRINTF(" first");
27 if (fp->fr_flags & FR_LOGORBLOCK)
28 PRINTF(" or-block");
29 if (fp->fr_loglevel != 0xffff) {
30 PRINTF(" level ");
31 s = fac_toname(fp->fr_loglevel);
32 if (s == NULL || *s == '\0')
33 s = "!!!";
34 u = pri_toname(fp->fr_loglevel);
35 if (u == NULL || *u == '\0')
36 u = "!!!";
37 PRINTF("%s.%s", s, u);
38 }
39}
